{"root":{"data":{"id":"djvo6m47cn40","created":1783765743933,"text":"地藏王\n梦魇力量:精神分裂:梦幻世界\n原身不知道身上有地藏王菩萨,甚至能转移宿主","font-size":16,"font-weight":"bold"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djvoh07yd2g0","created":1783766558276,"text":"十殿阎罗","layout":null,"font-weight":"bold","font-size":18},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djvo81o1oa80","created":1783765856149,"text":"1秦广王:专司人间寿夭生死，统管吉凶。善人直接接引，恶人交予其他各殿审判\n魂压,可轻易用自己精神力碾压对方,轻者眩晕,重者休克死亡","priority":null,"font-size":16,"layout":null},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"djvo8ofcwbs0","created":1783765905689,"text":"2楚江王:掌管活大地狱（寒冰地狱），惩罚在阳间伤人肢体、奸盗杀生等罪\n截脉:被影响者失去自身对某一器官的控制,比如心跳呼吸,四肢失去控制","priority":null,"font-size":16,"layout":null},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"djvo8wymbcg0","created":1783765924268,"text":"3宋帝王:掌管黑绳大地狱，惩罚阳间忤逆尊长、背信弃义、教唆兴讼等罪","priority":null,"font-size":16,"layout":null},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"djvo9ml3frs0","created":1783765980048,"text":"4五官王:掌管合大地狱（血池地狱），惩罚阳间逃税、欺诈、耍赖欠租等罪","priority":null,"font-size":16,"layout":null},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"djvoaatx5k80","created":1783766032823,"text":"5阎罗王:掌管叫唤大地狱。传说他本居第一殿，因怜悯屈死者而屡放还阳，被降调至此","font-size":16,"layout":null},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"djvoaicnji00","created":1783766049194,"text":"6卞城王:掌管大叫唤大地狱及枉死城，惩罚阳间怨天尤人、不敬神佛等罪","layout":null,"font-size":16},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"djvocdpzsl40","created":1783766195845,"text":"7泰山王:掌管热恼大地狱，惩罚阳间取尸骨制药、离间他人至亲等罪","layout":null,"font-size":16},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"djvocojmzzk0","created":1783766219405,"text":"8都市王:掌管大热恼大地狱，惩罚阳间不孝父母翁姑等罪","layout":null,"font-size":16},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"djvoddzozsg0","created":1783766274795,"text":"9平等王:掌管阿鼻大地狱，惩罚阳间杀人放火等极恶之罪","font-size":16,"layout":null},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"djvodn3vaag0","created":1783766294639,"text":"10转轮王:审核各殿解来的鬼魂，令其饮下孟婆汤，再经转轮台发往四大部洲投胎","font-size":16,"layout":null},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"djvohgr18og0","created":1783766594259,"text":"各类鬼差","font-size":18,"font-weight":"bold","layout":null},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djvohrvs5uo0","created":1783766618490,"text":"1文判官","font-size":16,"layout":null},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"djvoi3buhmg0","created":1783766643406,"text":"2武判官","font-size":16,"layout":null},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"djvoi698ysg0","created":1783766649780,"text":"3钟馗","font-size":16,"layout":null},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"djvoigi6h1k0","created":1783766672087,"text":"4黑无常","font-size":16,"layout":null},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"djvoizpeg8g0","created":1783766713883,"text":"5白无常","font-size":16,"layout":null},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"djvoj7y18f40","created":1783766731819,"text":"6日游神","font-size":16,"layout":null},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"djvojd81b480","created":1783766743308,"text":"7夜游神","font-size":16,"layout":null},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"djvojhbpwpc0","created":1783766752238,"text":"8牛头","font-size":16,"layout":null},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"djvojtb8sr40","created":1783766778330,"text":"9马面","font-size":16,"layout":null},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"djvok39v4k00","created":1783766800015,"text":"10鸟嘴","font-size":16,"layout":null},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"djvokacusm80","created":1783766815433,"text":"11鱼鳃","font-size":16,"layout":null},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"djvokdfmtqg0","created":1783766822131,"text":"12豹尾","font-size":16,"layout":null},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"djvokozye6o0","created":1783766847305,"text":"13蜂针","font-size":16,"layout":null},"children":[]}]}]},"template":"default","theme":"wire","version":"1.4.43"}